\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0ffc83af-070f-4d80-a915-596607510ee8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0ffc83af-070f-4d80-a915-596607510ee8\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMDNfMTUx/MDAxNjY3NDM4NjMzNDgx.HNI7XvriJxZfqsgiZmynpSQL9PhUg2-lA5IM9B_l2Dog.Ea74nSy83Q42p8NnOqfhFPBsGwl_Ts1iTGN09yumh4Qg.PNG.cookthedesign/01_A4_3%EB%8B%A8_%EB%B2%95%EB%AC%B4_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3780\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3309\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMDNfMTUx/MDAxNjY3NDM4NjMzNDgx.HNI7XvriJxZfqsgiZmynpSQL9PhUg2-lA5IM9B_l2Dog.Ea74nSy83Q42p8NnOqfhFPBsGwl_Ts1iTGN09yumh4Qg.PNG.cookthedesign/01_A4_3%EB%8B%A8_%EB%B2%95%EB%AC%B4_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ed26b68-2d37-49b8-8f96-3c8c4cd642c2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b12df3a4-3edc-40a3-8665-a213417df57b\" style=\"\">사이즈 설명</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fdd30c42-793b-4f2f-bde5-1070f0610abc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2e95df87-061f-4a0c-8467-470518802690\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-68903f6d-bf97-45e0-bc4d-72a9ef318aa7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a4cef970-416c-4608-a276-47e7ecfb1cba\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a879e70c-00f1-446f-81bd-e5010705f9e9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">사이즈는 접지시 접는 부분을 약간 적게 디자인하셔야 접었을때 사이즈가 이상없이 접을 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b432cd0-6f15-4cb1-9998-e002b06af055\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a58c41de-b477-4bdf-abb0-1f12a885bef7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">세로는 210mm로 고정하고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fad64487-2e3e-46d0-a838-5ad453fc8801\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3c279b6d-8b5f-4179-8756-6b3538c34407\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">가로는 297mm을 3등분하되(99mm) 제일 안쪽에 접히는 면은 98mm로 1mm 적게 디자인합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1c16481d-5ef5-4b70-bd8c-4e406a035100\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ef14e568-322f-4939-b41f-5bf9c90db630\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">보통 A4는 기본 수량이 4,000매입니다. 일반적인 아트지/스노우지 종이에 양면인쇄 후 3단접지하고 오시까지해서 잘 접히게 하면서 4,000매 제작하는것이 가장 일반적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-61daf018-8b35-4633-a301-b1e96c298fcb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4a51873e-95d1-46b0-a7e7-9fc92b4ecfef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0c4640d5-5168-4eb7-9729-18b2baa6486f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F222917932995#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
